{"about_the_game":"Step into the shoes of 'new_user', an engineer tasked with the monumental challenge of repairing machines to escape from an unknown location. Your tool? The fundamental building blocks of digital logic: complementary transistors.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUILD YOUR OWN PARTS</h2>Begin with the basics of electronic components, creating gates out of complementary transistors. Learn the art of electronic design as you progress from simple NAND and NOR gates to complex circuits capable of performing intricate tasks.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/Build.gif?t=1736083586\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ASSEMBLE THEM</h2>Combine your gates into larger, more sophisticated parts. Each assembly is a puzzle, demanding not just intelligence but creativity, planning, and foresight.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/Assemble.gif?t=1736083586\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OPTIMIZE</h2>Optimize your designs for efficiency and space, pushing the limits of your engineering prowess.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/Optimize.gif?t=1736083586\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TERMINALS</h2>All electronics seem non-functional, and they are your only way forward.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/Screen.gif?t=1736083586\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIND YOUR WAY OUT</h2>Advance into a strange world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/WayOutDescription.png?t=1736083586\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Open the door","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2844290/8265e868a1c81442d624685e2505c143b71ed257.jpg"},{"name":"NAND Designer","path":"