4290/extras/Assemble.gif?t=1736083586\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OPTIMIZE</h2>Optimize your designs for efficiency and space, pushing the limits of your engineering prowess.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/Optimize.gif?t=1736083586\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TERMINALS</h2>All electronics seem non-functional, and they are your only way forward.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/Screen.gif?t=1736083586\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIND YOUR WAY OUT</h2>Advance into a strange world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/WayOutDescription.png?t=1736083586\" />","developers":["Elorth"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/header.jpg?t=1736083586","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257006324,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257006324/movie480.mp4?t=1709996586","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257006324/movie_max.mp4?t=1709996586"},"name":"Gameplay trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257006324/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1709996586","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257006324/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1709996586","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257006324/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1